headline: Unitil (UTL) Beats Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: Unitil (UTL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 2.11% and 12.07%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
